# Jack1424 PRIVACY POLICY

Last Revised: 4/11/2023

Our privacy policy applies to information we collect when you use or access our website, application, or just interact with us. We may change this privacy policy from time to time. Whenever we make changes to this privacy policy, the changes are effective one month after we post the revised privacy policy (as indicated by revising the date at the top of our privacy policy). We encourage you to review our privacy policy whenever you access our services to stay informed about our information practices and the ways you can help protect your privacy.

## Collection of Information

By default, CreeperBot only has access to new messages as they are sent. In addition, CreeperBot can access basic Discord server information such as name and member count. This data will occasionally be polled for statistical purposes but will not be stored.

Jack1424 is not responsible for maintaining bot permissions on your server.

## Use of Information

The limited amount of information collected is used to monitor the use of CreeperBot an ensure that the current infrastructure supporting CreeperBot is sufficient to sustain a positive user experience.

## Sharing of Information

Information collected will only be viewed by Jack1424 and will not be viewed/stored by any other parties.

## Security

We take reasonable measures to help protect personal information from loss, theft, misuse and unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration and destruction.

## Contact Us

If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us by openening an issue on GitHub.
